OL,3,CWrexham community raising money and
OL,4,Cdonations for victims of Polish floods
OL,6,FAn urgent donation drive has begun in
OL,7,FWrexham to get essential items like
OL,8,Fclothing and toiletries to people in
OL,9,FPoland, in the wake of fatal floods.
OL,11,FDevastating weather hit parts of
OL,12,Fcentral Europe over the weekend, and
OL,13,Fthousands were told to evacuate their
OL,14,Fhomes, as five times the average
OL,15,Frainfall for September fell across the
OL,16,Farea.
