OL,3,CWrexham community raising money and
OL,4,Cdonations for victims of Polish floods
OL,6,FIn Wrexham, where there's a large
OL,7,FPolish community, the Polish
OL,8,FIntegration Support Centre is
OL,9,Fappealing for aid they can transport
OL,10,Fto Poland over the coming days.
OL,12,FAnna Buckley, the centre's Director
OL,13,Ftold us about a conversation she had
OL,14,Fwith a woman in Poland.
OL,16,F"The lady said to me: Anna I don't
OL,17,Fthink I will have anything, any place
OL,18,Fwhere I can come back, because I don't
OL,19,Fknow where our house is, everything is
OL,20,Fflooded, it's like a massive river."
