OL,3,CWrexham community raising money and
OL,4,Cdonations for victims of Polish floods
OL,6,FAnna said: "I can only imagine, the
OL,7,Fpeople, they haven't only lost their
OL,8,Fhouse, they lost their hope, they lost
OL,9,Ftheir belongings, they lost their
OL,10,Fheritage, and if someone lost their
OL,11,Fmum and dad, they can't find them, so
OL,12,FI think when the water goes down, then
OL,13,Fthe real disaster will happen."
OL,15,FAnne Greenlees is a volunteer at the
OL,16,Fcentre, she says: "We need everything.
OL,18,F"Can you imagine? If I imagine, if my
OL,19,Fhome was obliterated, what would I
OL,20,Factually need, I'd need everything.
