OL,3,CWrexham community raising money and
OL,4,Cdonations for victims of Polish floods
OL,6,FDawn Roberts McCabe from the
OL,7,FAssociation of Voluntary Organisations
OL,8,FWrexham said: "The flooding their
OL,9,Fmeans so much more because they don't
OL,10,Fhave the infrastructure we have here
OL,11,Fin the UK, they don't have the
OL,12,Fresponse system we have, and they
OL,13,Fdon't have the insurance systems in
OL,14,Fplace to help them recover when this
OL,15,Fis over so my heart really goes out to
OL,16,Fthem right now."
OL,18,FThe centre is well-prepared for the
OL,19,Ftask, having sent out around 80
OL,20,Florries and raised more than #4
OL,21,Fmillion for Ukraine.
