OL,3,CWrexham community raising money and
OL,4,Cdonations for victims of Polish floods
OL,6,FThey're hoping for a similar response
OL,7,Fto to flooding crisis in Poland.
OL,9,F"Each lorry to Poland costs me two
OL,10,Fthousand pounds," said Anna. "It
OL,11,Fdepends which area, but between two
OL,12,Fthousand and three thousand pounds, it
OL,13,Fdepends how far they have to go, and I
OL,14,Fwant to send at least ten."
OL,16,FThe hope is the public will respond,
OL,17,Fso aid can get to the victims.
